Renaming Custom Settings Banks


Rename selected custom settings banks.


1 SelectI.Q. IMAGE QUALITY SETTING > EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING in the shooting menu and press MENU/OK.
This assumes that you wish to rename settings for still phy. To rename movie settings, navigate to □ MOVIE SETTING in the movie menus and select EDIT/SAVE 2 Highlight the desired custom set- tings bank and press MENU/OK.photogra- CUSTOM SETTING. I.Q. EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING AF MF C1 CUSTOM 1 · C2 CUSTOM 2 々 CUSTOM 3 C3 8
3 Highlight EDIT CUSTOM NAME and press MENU/OK.C4 CUSTOM 4 C5 CUSTOM 5 M C6 CUSTOM 6 BACK] EXIT I.Q. CUSTOM 1 C1 SAVE CURRENT SETTINGS EDIT/CHECK SAVE THE CHANGES RESET THE CHANGES COPY
RESET CUSTOM SETTING EDIT CUSTOM NAME BACK EXIT
4 Enter a new name for the custom settings bank and SET.select
The selected bank will be renamed.
